data.description: Welcome to the charming Rose Gardens neighborhood! This impressive brick home has 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths, cozy living room, formal dining room, and delightful eat-in kitchen. Additionally, you'll find a generously sized detached garage/workshop with power, great for all your DIY projects. Parking is a breeze with an extra-wide and deep driveway that can accommodate multiple vehicles, a camper, or even a boat. For those seeking a serene escape, there's a small, bright, and earthy 4-season sunroom, great for relaxing and enjoying the outdoors year-round. Rest easy knowing this charming home is equipped with a new electrical system and water heater. The sellers also installed a security system, water softener, and garbage disposal. Located just minutes away from Wards Corner, Military bases, and the interstate, this home offers convenience at its finest. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful home yours. Some photos virtually staged.
